# PII strings to redact — one per line
# Lines starting with # are ignored
# The script searches every page of every PDF for exact matches of these strings
# and redacts all occurrences.
#
# Tips:
#   - Add each part of an address as a separate line in case they appear
#     on different lines in the document
#   - Include common variations (with and without middle initial, etc.)
#   - Matching is case-sensitive, so add the version that appears in the PDFs

John Smith
J. Smith
123 Main Street
Anytown
AB1 2CD
john.smith@example.com
